<note n="0324003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0324003">秤＝稱【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0324004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0324004">（得）＋不【三】【宮】</note>
